snippet.title: Eighth Era Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Real heroes play for keeps. Are you in?

Eighth Era is the first mobile squad RPG where players compete for the chance to win real collectibles.

Play now in Canada or join the waitlist for worldwide: https://eighthera.onelink.me/hKZ7/yt
